{"tid":1879692,"cid":21,"subCid":8,"title":"【古典音樂】教你彈琴","createTime":"2020-02-14T10:40:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-20T18:08:35.000Z","uid":103385,"like":12,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"925e20768dd620261f75911ff476c90302e43145","tid":1879692,"uid":103385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:40:35.000Z","msg":"停課停到2046，對好多音樂從業者黎講除咗收入大減之外，重點係悶到仆街，呢排真係多咗好多時間，反正都係冇嘢做，決定攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />直接教大家彈琴。<br />\n<br />\n但基本睇譜／樂理層面各樣就唔教啦，網上已經有無限嘅資源，所以會教大家一啲真係實戰應用到嘅彈琴／練琴小技巧，比較適合本身已經有一定程度嘅巴絲打。<br />\n<br />\n唔一定百分百正確，當係小小分享，有啲idea會通用喺所有樂器，但我主要會用鋼琴示範，希望幫到不論係學定係教緊古典音樂嘅大家。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我將所有片放咗喺我Studio IG（會有我大個，柒撚親就講聲唔好意思先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/yins_music?igshid=nmq6lkjd5ztc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fyins_music%3Figshid%3Dnmq6lkjd5ztc&d=NEgIrN0XKBZxjsPVzjJKR%2BdFAmKeyJhstBKVrdqrVyA%3D&h=140b8b43\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/yins_music?igshid=nmq6lkjd5ztc</a><br />\n不定期更新，有咩疑問或者想我講嘅Topic都可以直接DM我（但唔洗問我教唔教琴，以我經驗大人學生如果唔係修音樂嘅通常都係學兩學就收皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"4f61ef9d09f871d637c0e437570d410628e763c3","tid":1879692,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:42:47.000Z","msg":"巴打好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01b6df4ac35678c92e062444076b56da74e17794","tid":1879692,"uid":228143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-14T10:45:51.000Z","msg":"今晚有花花睇"},{"pid":"82a37c73b4e913f5604e25157f9f5408657d14c7","tid":1879692,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4f61ef9d09f871d637c0e437570d410628e763c3","tid":1879692,"uid":124400,"like":1,"dislike"