到你嘅技巧，所以暫時都應該唔會講最初階嘅嘢住啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3b184979d24cc70cb78c8c29d1b138b5937a108","tid":1879692,"uid":288086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"Long trill點練？<br />\nBach Invention"},{"pid":"937d4490a3e67c9ea0f506d4c69caa6470fe51e0","tid":1879692,"uid":103385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b184979d24cc70cb78c8c29d1b138b5937a108","tid":1879692,"uid":288086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"Long trill點練？<br />\nBach Invention"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:34:19.000Z","msg":"彈trill用邊兩隻手指同埋用邊度發力各方面都好影響，當你雙白鍵trill用13就會輕鬆啲囉，我遲啲都會講下，但Bach invention唔明你想問乜？"},{"pid":"522225ab5254df97cf78fbbf8907c85b50061c7c","tid":1879692,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:29:18.000Z","msg":"CHING 好搞笑<br />\n拍多D 片"},{"pid":"c101f0f14cc3bf7663793aa0514c921c89a44d57","tid":1879692,"uid":190369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:34:28.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c621eae1b9d64fe32a2767d0a0b7401efb44f5f3","tid":1879692,"uid":27793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:40:50.000Z","msg":"好搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一入到ig全部大頭<br />\n好勇"},{"pid":"6ba3530be11abddd900f3d7b05b42ef32d33c1b8","tid":1879692,"uid":288086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"937d4490a3e67c9ea0f506d4c69caa6470fe51e0","tid":1879692,"uid":103385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d3b184979d24cc70cb78c8c29d1b138b5937a108","tid":1879692,"uid":288086,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T06:39:20.000Z","msg":"Long trill點練？<br />\nBach Invention"},"citedBy":1,"r